S.FORM: Elmer Bennett ( NBA ) Elmer Bennett ( NBA ) Elmer Bennett nalecuhan i Evanston, Illinois, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Elmer Bennett i 1992 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 38, namapili' tu nu Atlanta Hawks putiput. 2 bulad 13 demiad, 1970 a mihca, Elmer Bennett, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
